41
00:03:13,071 --> 00:03:19,993
character usually, and we call that the player character. The player character is given tools

42
00:03:20,373 --> 00:03:24,975
where they are able to act upon the world. We sometimes call these verbs or interacts.

43
00:03:26,998 --> 00:03:29,640
