78
00:05:18,874 --> 00:05:24,899
Chloe is far more toward the Kratos end of the spectrum than Max is, and this makes sense

79
00:05:25,040 --> 00:05:28,222
because Chloe began her life as an NPC in the original game.

80
00:05:28,282 --> 00:05:30,925
