00:10:49,138 --> 00:10:52,019
the most compelling narrative movement to the scene.

166
00:10:53,980 --> 00:10:58,122
And that relationship between the player and Chloe

167
00:10:58,822 --> 00:11:03,985
in this moment shifts from spectator and subject

168
00:11:04,965 --> 00:11:05,866
to a real alignment.

169
00:11:07,126 --> 00:11:08,787
