178
00:11:40,663 --> 00:11:42,183
And we realized that there's a power

179
00:11:42,303 --> 00:11:45,404
to interactive storytelling in terms of its ability

180
00:11:45,824 --> 00:11:49,186
to engender empathy that we didn't really understand.

