00:12:11,545 --> 00:12:16,790
because of experiencing Chloe's journey. That humbled us and blew us away and so

187
00:12:17,651 --> 00:12:22,195
ultimately led us to wanting to make a game about empathy.

188
00:12:27,560 --> 00:12:28,401
Yeah, so we were

189
00:12:29,500 --> 00:12:34,503
fascinated by those letters we received, the reactions we received, by this extension of

190
00:12:34,603 --> 00:12:40,546
empathy to all different kinds of people into, as we laid out, this really singular character

