201
00:13:22,320 --> 00:13:24,141
This time she's named Alex,

202
00:13:24,642 --> 00:13:27,464
and the player is going to control her the entire game

203
00:13:27,624 --> 00:13:28,685
to interact with the world.

204
00:13:29,926 --> 00:13:32,809
We get to explore as her, hear her thoughts, make choices,

205
00:13:33,349 --> 00:13:35,111
but now we wanted to extend

206
00:13:35,291 --> 00:13:37,473
that player character experience outward.

207
00:13:37,673 --> 00:13:40,435
So we came up with this empathy power for Alex

208
00:13:40,455 --> 00:13:41,876
that functioned like a prism,

209
00:13:42,397 --> 00:13:46,120
projecting us through her into the interior spaces

210
00:13:46,440 --> 00:13:47,981
of the NPCs in the world around her.

211
00:13:52,465 --> 00:13:57,108
It starts with auras, showing us that an NPC is feeling an emotion,

212
00:13:57,369 --> 00:14:00,971
and when we use our empathy power, we're rewarded with the NPC's thoughts

213
00:14:01,212 --> 00:14:03,593
in their voice about the emotion that they're feeling.

214
00:14:04,354 --> 00:14:06,756
And we actually discovered something really interesting

215
00:14:06,876 --> 00:14:08,677
while we were writing these NPC insights.

216
00:14:09,518 --> 00:14:11,340
Players enjoyed hearing them,

217
00:14:11,620 --> 00:14:14,322
but with all the different voices coming into their head,

